# Add to nginx `add_header Content-Security-Policy` for SynqDrive SPA.
# Required for @didit-protocol/sdk-web modal iframe (verify.didit.me).
#
# Without frame-src, browsers fall back to default-src 'self' and block the Didit overlay iframe
# (dark backdrop visible, empty modal — appears "hung").
#
# Example tail of CSP directive:
#   ... worker-src 'self' blob:; frame-src 'self' https://verify.didit.me https://verification.didit.me https://*.didit.me;
